Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.76,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:19.65,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:24.82,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:30.59,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:36.66,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:40.45,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:48.77,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:54.25,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.15,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:22:05.22,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}maybe it wasn't 'cause \Nyou're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:10.84,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:16.38,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:21.71,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:26.89,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:34.26,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}your warm hand
